for initialising TailWind

    1. run command "npm init -y
            this will create a "package.json" in the project

    2. add " "type": "module"," in the "package.json" file after main

    3. run "npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/cli" 
            this will install TailWind packages 
            you can also check dependencies in "package.json" file to confirm

    4. run "npx @tailwindcss/cli -i src/main/resources/static/css/input.css -o src/main/resources/static/css/output.css"
            this will create output.css file at the provided location
            and we need output.css file for styling





